Our governance and policies for corporate citizenship Responsibility for selecting and managing non-profit and

socially impactful activities lies with the local departments or management teams in each country. This approach helps to provide support and create value where it is needed most. Simultaneously, we combine in-depth local knowledge with long-term commitment to overcome social challenges that vary from region to region.